Package: nacre
Title: Fine-Grained Reactive DOM Bindings for Shiny
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Kyle", "Husmann", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "khusmann@gmail.com")
Description: A thin rendering layer on top of Shiny that replaces renderUI
    with Solid-style fine-grained DOM bindings. Pass a function instead of a
    value to make any tag attribute reactive.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    shiny,
    htmltools
Suggests:
    DT
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://khusmann.github.io/nacre/
